General.Name: APB Resources Bhd
General.Description: APB Resources Berhad, an investment holding company, engages in the fabrication of design engineering equipment for petrochemical process, chemical, oil palm processing, paper mill, and power generation industries in Malaysia and internationally. The company operates through three segments: Fabrication, Non-Destructive Testing, and Others. It also provides non-destructive testing services and other related services; and fabricates finned tubes. APB Resources Berhad is based in Shah Alam, Malaysia.
